595_7049747370601371318_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=N2OYWSF5sKEQ7kNvgFW-9m0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYApSFxSVoMEQFjiuMeEboMOqaisnbtG-BYwnMGG3RMf3w&oe=6787916F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "BackToWork_Landscape.png", "id": "591444446866496", "uri": "https://scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031370_591444450199829_4187114230853943938_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IEYQ-5pii7sQ7kNvgHG01po&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAniSOKrRI-1OC4HcNjBRaZUPlJ3E_7yXN5y-qsfcG7WQ&oe=67879815"}, "display_name": "Monkey Doo", "keywords": ["free", "multiplayer", "gorilla", "social", "hangout"], "long_description": "# \ud83d\udda5\ufe0f\u2702\ufe0fBack to Work Update! \n\n- New player-designed office battle pass cosmetics **(Stapler doo, Phone head, Computer head, Pencil Hands, Sticky Notes head)**\n- New Sweet Dealz, including the highly requested Eyelashes\n\n=================================================\n\n{630466372754312}\n**About**\n# Live in the heart of the Bermuda Triangle with all your Monkey friends! Swing on vines, throw doo at your enemies, and climb everything! \n\n- Huge Maps: Explore the Bermuda Jungle, Floating Forests, Ancient Ruins, Lava Chasm, and more\n\n- Unique Gamemodes: Be the first to collect 10 bananas or work together to fend off hordes of crocs -- new modes are coming all the time\n\n- Monkey Apparel: Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo\n\n- Ruby Mines: Explore a seemingly endless set of tunnels filled with lore, new NPC's, and our Battle Pass! Unlock exclusive rewards like Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more with free and paid rewards! \n\nThemed Cosmetics & Hands-on Fun: Get your hands on... well, Hand cosmetics! Plus, a bunch of wacky, interactive items like things you can eat, press, and shake to your heart's content.\n\nHidden Treasures: Dive into a revamped store experience and hunt for secrets - like a mysterious portal leading to a hidden market. Plus, uncover new secrets via the plane!\n\nJump into the recently installed mining elevator to descend deep into the old ruby mines. Survive the **wrath of Xongo & save the Lost Souls** in Monkey Doo's all new Horror Mode!\n\n{9314948115205875}\n", "short_description": "\ud83d\udda5\ufe0f\u2702\ufe0fBack to Work Update! \n\nLive in the heart of the Bermuda Triangle with all your Monkey friends! Swing on vines, throw doo at your enemies, and climb everything! \n\n- Huge Maps: Explore the Bermuda Jungle, Floating Forests, Ancient Ruins, Lava Chasm, and more\n\n- Unique Gamemodes: Be the first to collect 10 bananas or explore the lost mines and save souls -- new modes are coming all the time!\n\n- Monkey Apparel: Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo"}]}, "developer_name": "Continuum XR", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.clique.games/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.clique.games/terms", "publisher_name": "Clique Games ", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.monkeydoovr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1023770785722696"}, {"id": "1990104051447093"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "SOCIAL", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8950507275057270"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image